This template creates a clear fix for floating elements.

== Usage ==
<pre>
{{Clear}}
{{Clear|left}}
{{Clear|right}}
{{Clear|both}}
</pre>

== Parameters ==
* '''1''' (optional): Clear direction (left, right, both). Default is both.

</noinclude><includeonly><div style="clear: {{#switch: {{{1|}}}
| left = left
| right = right
| both = both
| #default = both
}};"></div></includeonly>
